UID:OspBQMi0Cw-1j-LHsjC__
SUMMARY:Free Tax Help
DTSTAMP:20260326T004302Z
DTSTART:20260328T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:Saturday\, March 28\, 2026\, 10am - 1:30pm\n\nTrained volunteer
	s will be available to answer questions and prepare personal tax returns.\
	n\nLocation Link:\n\nBroadview Branch\n\nRoom Location: Meeting Room\n\nRe
	gistration Required: Registration is not required.\n\nDetailed Description
	: This service is free and available to individuals only. The free service
	 is not available for business tax returns. To receive tax help\, bring th
	e following documents:\,\n\nRequired:\n\nPhoto identification\, Social Sec
	urity cards or Individual Taxpayer Identification Numbers \\(ITIN\\) for e
	veryone listed on the tax return.\, Proof of income\, for example\, W2s an
	d 1099s \\(Social Security benefits\\)\, Official documents on Social Secu
	rity Administration letterhead\, Medicare card \\(if Social Security numbe
	r is followed by an "A"\\)\, Be prepared to provide information about heal
	th care coverage for each person on the return.\,\n\nRecommended:\n\nLast 
	year&'s tax return\, if available\, Bank account and routing numbers for d
	irect deposit of refunds\, Photocopies or computer print-outs of any of th
	ese documents willbe accepted.\, Due to federal budget cuts the IRS is una
	ble to provide the Library with certain tax forms and instruction booklets
	.\, Most IRS forms are available online at\n\nwww.irs.gov .\, You may make
	 free black-and-white prints of the forms from Library computers:\n\nwww.s
	pl.org/Print \, Thanks to our partner\n\nAARP .\n\nEvent Logistics: AARP T
	ax Help locations serve anyone who earned less than $80\,000 in 2025.\, Fo
	r eligibility details\, contact AARP at 888-227-7669.\n\nContact Us: If yo
	u have questions about this event\,\n\nAsk Us\n\nor call 206-386-4636.\n\n
	ADA Accommodations: We can provide accommodations for people with disabili
	ties at Library events. Please\n\ncontactLEAP\n\nat least seven days befor
	e the event to request accommodations.\, All Library programs are free and
	 open to the public.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/free
	-tax-help/18162991/2026-03-28T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - All Events
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/free-tax-help/18162991/20
	26-03-28T00
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-all
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - All Events
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT3H30M
END:VEVENT
