	ts. Families and visitors are encouraged to stroll the property\, keep an 
	eye out for the Easter Bunny’s appearances and join in the fun as he makes
	 his way around the center spreading springtime cheer. This event is free 
	of charge and open to the public\; no pre-registration is required to atte
